{"tid":1591851,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"同期勝率最差 球迷叫蘇B滾蛋","createTime":"2019-09-24T10:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T08:14:48.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"283194f8d044b2a48b6e6bb23ba4c20c7c367b5e","tid":1591851,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T10:37:31.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】曼聯上輪不敵韋斯咸後，領隊蘇斯克查被炒的呼聲，此起彼落。數據不說謊，看看他該不該炒。<br />\n<br />\n挪威籍領隊蘇斯克查（Ole Gunnar Solskjaer）日前駕車回到訓練場，被一群憤怒的魔迷高呼：「快些滾蛋」。當然，目標還有「罪魁禍首」活禾特。蘇B由上季入「魔」至今，總共領軍17場聯賽，成績是5勝4和8負，得勝率只有29%，創下後費格遜時代的新低。<br />\n<br />\n對比其他3任領隊，摩連奴和「師父」雲高爾的得勝率巧合相同，一樣是52%，最令人意外的是，反而被爵爺欽點的莫耶斯，頭17場取得10勝，得勝率有58%，難怪很多球迷開始為他呻冤。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提，費格遜上任的頭17場聯賽，其實得勝率低於摩連奴、雲高爾和莫耶斯，只有41%，卻在之後開創了紅魔王朝。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"0a654732fe8123f5c78b7edc2a4456be5297e4a8","tid":1591851,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T10:37:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"20da86e6c4de069938a86a3f92fdc37bd81354fa","tid":1591851,"uid":16659,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T10:39:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VuDuznS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVuDuznS.png&h=42423a06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21ca780d56afbf22de7a2c6b6b89544520ffd6da","tid":1591851,"uid":323393,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T10:41:30.000Z","msg":"佢當初應該學林伯玩青訓算<br />\n咁就算成績差都冇咁覺眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a8bbda6da006d0383d62a5c377872f015bc4b6","tid":1591851,"uid":14075,"like":8,"dislike":12,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:20:00.000Z","msg":"反而被爵爺欽點的莫耶斯，頭17